=============================================

================================

* **Reference Number**: cb-981-21098747
* **Solicitation Number**: W8482-242111/A
* **Publication Date**: 2024-01-26
* **Tender Closing Date**: 2024-05-15T14:00:00
* **Expected Contract Start Date**: 2024-03-06
* **Expected Contract End Date**: 2025-01-30

## Contract Description
================================

The Department of National Defence (DND) has issued a tender for the procurement of various spare items for Victoria-Class submarines. The tender includes the following items:

* **Log Probe Assembly (Item 1)**
	+ Quantity: 4
	+ Unit of Issue: EA
	+ Delivery Location: CFB Esquimalt
* **Log Probe Assembly (Item 2)**
	+ Quantity: 1
	+ Unit of Issue: EA
	+ Delivery Location: CFB Halifax
* **Plain Encased Seal (Item 5)**
	+ Quantity: 8
	+ Unit of Issue: EA
	+ Delivery Location: CFB Esquimalt
* **Plain Encased Seal (Item 6)**
	+ Quantity: 4
	+ Unit of Issue: EA
	+ Delivery Location: CFB Halifax
* **O-Ring (Item 7)**
	+ Quantity: 40
	+ Unit of Issue: EA
	+ Delivery Location: CFB Esquimalt
* **O-Ring (Item 8)**
	+ Quantity: 10
	+ Unit of Issue: EA
	+ Delivery Location: CFB Halifax
* **Capuchon Screw (Item 9)**
	+ Quantity: 80
	+ Unit of Issue: EA
	+ Delivery Location: CFB Esquimalt
* **Capuchon Screw (Item 10)**
	+ Quantity: 80
	+ Unit of Issue: EA
	+ Delivery Location: CFB Halifax
* **Ball Valve (Item 11)**
	+ Quantity: 10
	+ Unit of Issue: EA
	+ Delivery Location: CFB Esquimalt
